                <span class="icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="accordion-content">
                <p>
                    As soon as our team has received you kit and sorted through, this can take up to 7 buisness days
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion-item">
            <button id="accordion-button-3" aria-expanded="false">
                <span class="accordion-title">I've sent my tidy kit, what next?</span>
                <span class="icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="accordion-content">
                <p>
                    We'll send you and email once our courier has scanned the parcel. From here we will sort through and email you once your credits have been added to your account.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion-item">
            <button id="accordion-button-4" aria-expanded="false">
                <span class="accordion-title">What items are acceptable for the kits?</span>
                <span class="icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="accordion-content">
                <p>
                            Almost anything! Most items are able to be reused, recycled or repurposed in someway. Hower for hygenic reasoons we do not except undergarments and most swimwear. Contact us if you have any specific querys
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion-item">
            <button id="accordion-button-5" aria-expanded="false">
                <span class="accordion-title">What happens to the items in the kits?</span>
                <span class="icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="accordion-content">
                <p>
                    They will be resold, recycled or repurposed. Visit our How We Recyle page for more information
                </p>
